<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Handit.AI Alert</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 30px;
        background: #ffffff url('cid:bg-image') no-repeat top center;
        background-size: cover;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }

      .logo {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        width: 180px;
        height: auto;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #00272f;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #00272f;
        margin: 12px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #02f7aa;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #02f7aa;
        color: #00272f !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #00272f;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #00272f;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
          width: 100px;
          margin-top: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img class="logo" src="cid:logo-image" alt="Handit.ai Logo" />
      
      <h1>Automated Evaluation Alert</h1>
      <p>We've identified a potential issue during the latest automated evaluation. Please review the details below:</p>

      <p><span class="label">Agent:</span> {{agent_name}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Node:</span> {{node_name}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Summary:</span><br />{{{reviewer_summary}}}</p>

      <a href="{{tracing_url}}" class="button">Review in Dashboard</a>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} Handit.ai â€” Monitoring and optimizing AI systems in real time.<br />
        <a href="mailto:contact@handit.ai">contact@handit.ai</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
